org.bukkit.potion

クラス PotionEffectType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.potion.PotionEffectType
  • 直系の既知のサブクラス:
    PotionEffectTypeWrapper

    public abstract class PotionEffectType
extends Object
    Represents a type of potion and its effect on an entity.
